{"tid":1831240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： CCTVB直播喪避「光復」手勢 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-01-20T08:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c959e4ee3d291aa2a388bf47f0c9c3b39cb3cfb1","tid":1831240,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200120/NDRHCTPWGY66WMZGD36R2BY64I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200120%2FNDRHCTPWGY66WMZGD36R2BY64I%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9z632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=da627d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200120%2FNDRHCTPWGY66WMZGD36R2BY64I%2F&h=7b46d8c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200120/NDRHCTPWGY66WMZGD36R2BY64I/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\nCCTVB直播喪避「光復」手勢 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200120/large/1579451361_4f89.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579451361_4f89.gif&h=4a6d2476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n早排TVB投訴話去採訪反送中遊行時候遭人阻攔，威脅新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭影地下後熄機<br />\n<br />\n噚晚維園年宵開鑼，TVB新聞有派人去現場做直播，今次冇示威者、冇市民阻攔採訪，但TVB個直播做做吓竟然要將個鏡頭影落地下，之後仲cut埋直播！為乜事呢？原來係唔想影到現場市民做「五大訴求、缺一不可」手勢（圖左）。<br />\n<br />\n話說TVB記者徐子瀅喺維園年宵做現場直播，今次絕對冇市民阻攔佢哋採訪，不過有市民經過鏡頭前，即刻舉起五隻同一隻手指，做「五大訴求、缺一不可」手勢，又有市民指住自己頂「光復香港」帽，亦有拎住反送中揮春行過，八方見個鏡頭不斷左閃右避，總之就唔畀呢啲畫面入鏡，後來避無可避，竟然將個鏡頭影落地下，仲即cut埋直播。其實八方睇到條片，市民都係過鏡式行過，完全冇影響個直播，CCTVB使唔使怕成咁呢？"},{"pid":"0cc51bd565d9722027a51970a4b3e26d48f39002","tid":1831240,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"有冇得扮跑撞爆佢部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7910c28055ccb92e1fb